n, shared with these scholars his ideological struggle between his love for Torah study and "hokhmah" (philosophy, wisdom).  This Grand Epistle reveals much about this towering figure and provides a moving portrait of him during his last decade.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 29. Feb 2020) 4aCode of Jewish Law. 4aEpistolary compositions. 4aHokhmah. 4aIggeret. 4aLate Middle Ages. 4aMaimonides. 4aMiddle Ages. 4aMishneh Torah. 4aScholars of Lunel. 4aSephardic poetic style. 4aTanakh. 4aTorah. 7aRELIGION / Judaism / Sacred Writings.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertASP eBook Package 2019z978311068819108iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2019 Englishz978311061076508iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2019z9783110664232oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Theol., Relig. Stud., Jewish Stud.2019 Englishz978311061074108iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Theology, Relig. Studies, Jewish Studies 2019z9783110606508oZDB-23-DGF40uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/9781618119629zCo-access DOI >> click Walter de Gruyter423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/cover/covers/9781618119629.jpg  a978-3-11-061074-1  EBOOK PACKAGE Theol., Relig. Stud., Jewish Stud.2019 Englishb2019  a978-3-11-061076-5  EBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2019 Englishb2019  a978-3-11-068819-1  ASP eBook Package 2019b2019  aEBA_CL_PLTLJSIS  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_ECL_PLTLJSIS  aEBA_EEBKALL  aEBA_ESSHALL  aEBA_PPALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA13ENGE  aPDA14ALL  aPDA16SSH  aPDA17SSHEE  aPDA1ALL  aPDA2  aPDA2HUM  aPDA5EBK  aPDA7ENG  aZDB-23-DGFb2019  aZDB-23-DGGb2019